<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CF Healthnet OTP Verification</title>
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container" style="max-width: 600px;margin: 0 auto;background-color: #ffffff;box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);">
        <div class="header" style="background-color: #f7f9fc;padding: 30px 0;text-align: center;border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e8f5;">
            <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dwaqh1nvr/image/upload/v1737585966/cosmic_forge_logo_4_cinopk.png" alt="CF Healthnet Logo" style="height: 40px;width: auto;">
        </div>
        
        <div class="content" style="padding: 40px 50px;line-height: 1.6;">
            <h1 style="color: #1a56db;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 25px;font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;">CF Healthnet</h1>
            
            <p class="greeting" style="margin: 0 0 20px;color: #2d3748;font-size: 18px;font-weight: 500;">Hi there, <%= data.email  %></p>
            
            <p style="margin: 0 0 20px;color: #4a5568;font-size: 16px;">To proceed further with your registration process on CF HealthNet please use the OTP below</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container" style="margin: 30px 0;text-align: center;padding: 20px;background-color: #f0f7ff;border-radius: 8px;border-left: 4px solid #1a56db;">
                <div class="otp-code" style="font-family: monospace;font-size: 32px;font-weight: 700;color: #1a56db;letter-spacing: 4px;background: #ffffff;padding: 10px 20px;border-radius: 6px;border: 1px solid #d1ddf7;display: inline-block;"><%= data.otp %></div>
                <div class="time-notice" style="font-size: 14px;color: #718096;margin-top: 15px;font-style: italic;">Please note that this OTP will only be valid for 5 minutes</div>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin: 0 0 20px;color: #4a5568;font-size: 16px;">Regards,<br>CF HealthNet</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer" style="background-color: #f5f8ff;padding: 30px 50px;font-size: 14px;color: #718096;line-height: 1.6;border-top: 1px solid #e1e8f5;">
            <div class="company-info" style="margin-top: 25px;padding-top: 20px;border-top: 1px solid #e1e8f5;">
                CosmicForge HealthNet Limited, is an expanding digital health platform dedicated to revolutionizing the way healthcare is accessed and provided throughout Africa.
                <br><br>
                <a href="https://cfhealthnet.com" class="cta-button" style="display: inline-block;background-color: #1a56db;text-decoration: none;padding: 12px 30px;border-radius: 6px;font-weight: 600;margin: 20px 0;text-align: center;color: white !important;">Learn More</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="unsubscribe" style="margin-top: 20px;font-size: 12px;color: #a0aec0;">
                You are receiving this email because you signed up on CF HealthNet. 
                <a href="#" style="color: #1a56db;text-decoration: none;">Unsubscribe</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
